            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I recently visited VGN Chinmaya Vidyalaya near my residence. I liked the ambience of the school. However, I quickly realized that securing admission wasn’t easy, as the process was strictly merit-based, with no room for recommendations. My child underwent an entrance exam, and the results were published on time with complete transparency, including a detailed breakdown of marks for parents. I was truly pleased to enroll my child in this school that upholds strong values and fairness in its admission process.",
          "publisher": {
